title: Joyful Daily Stitching, Seam by Seam - Complete Guide to 500 Emb
description: Joyful Daily Stitching, Seam by Seam - Complete Guide to 500 Embroidery-Stitch Combinations, Perfect for Crazy Quilting English | 354 pages | EPUB | 83 MB http://4kw.in/13202.html Valerie Bothell encourages readers to stitch daily, even for a few minutes. If you can stitch one seam 5 days a week, over the course of a year readers will complete 250 seams! The book includes instructions for 61 basic embroidery stitches and over 500 seam-treatment stitch combinations, as well as crazy-quilt-block piecing instructions and information about tools and supplies
